shape: sequence_diagram

nsd: NSD
nsc: NSC main loop
a: VipAllocator
r: NscRouter
d: DnsRecords
p: ProxyManager

nsd -> nsc: "SSE routing_config (routes[])"

loop_routes: for each route {
  nsc -> a: allocate(route.site)
  a -> nsc: vip (127.11.x.x)
  nsc -> r: update_routing → insert sites_by_name/vip + routes
  nsc -> d: insert(route.domain.lower → vip)
}

nsc -> p: proxy_mgr.update()
p -> p: 对新 (VIP, port) 启动 TCP listener

note: 进程退出 → 所有状态丢失 (ephemeral)
